symbol library: Hardware/KiCad/plataVM_symbols.kicad_sym
controller: LM5143A-Q1 RHA-40, 40 physical pins + EP
MOSFET: BUK9Y6R0-60E LFPAK56/SOT669
MOSFET physical pins: 1=S, 2=S, 3=S, 4=G, mb=D
exact MOSFET instances: 4
shunt: WSK25125L000FEA / WSK2512 four-terminal
shunt terminals: I1/I2 current; E1/E2 voltage sense
exact Kelvin shunt instances: 2
per-phase Kelvin sense nets: RSHx_SENSE_HI / RSHx_SENSE_LO
production footprints assigned: 0
exact symbol Gate: PASS
native converter-core internal topology: PASS (verified before materialized commit)
RESULT: PASS
NOTE: owner KiCad 10 hierarchy/open-save/visual review remains mandatory.
""",
        encoding="utf-8",
    )

    AMENDMENT.write_text(
        """# PCB-D POWER_5V — exact discrete physical pin-map amendment V1.9

Дата: 2026-07-24  
Gate: `Q-P5-019C1`  
Статус: `CLOSED_EXACT_DISCRETE_PINMAP_NATIVE_INTERNAL_ERC_PASS`

## 1. Причина amendment

Owner visual review выявил, что controller symbol был exact, но силовые MOSFETs и Kelvin-шунты оставались generic symbols. Это было допустимо до footprint Gate, но недостаточно для физически проверяемой схемы.

## 2. Официальный physical contract

